title: Museum Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Macrobiotic, Organic, Raw, Salad bar
description: A vegetarian cafe serving mostly raw and organic food, including vegan options. Offers lunch (salad, soup, sandwiches), cakes and coffee. Please note that you can eat at the cafe without paying for admission to the museum if you choose.
streetAddress: Haigh Terrace, The National Maritime Museum of Ireland
